    "MissionGiver": "XenoThreat",
    "Title": "Total Server Wipe",
    "Description": "One of our datarunners went MIA while transporting vital operational information. A few hours ago, we determined that they were hit by a Headhunter raiding party and the contents of the ship\u2019s datastores were transferred to their servers at ~mission(location|address). \n\nWhile we have every reason to believe that our encryption will hold, we cannot take the risk that the contents of those files will be exposed. You are being ordered to head there and ensure our data remains private by destroying the Headhunter servers.\n\nI strongly encourage thoroughness. Raze everything and everyone you can to the ground.\n\nComm. Spec. Engler",
